text: Wellington Phoenix Women's Football Club is a New Zealand women's football club based in Wellington. It is the female equivalent of Wellington Phoenix FC. The club competes in the A-League Women, being the only New Zealand club in the league (the rest are from Australia). ==References== Category:A-League Women Category:Football clubs in New Zealand Wellington Phoenix FC (A-League Women) Category:2021 establishments Category:2020s establishments in Oceania Category:21st-century establishments in New Zealand
